## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
uv sync --all-groups

# Run the server
uv run uvicorn app.main:app --reload

# Run tests
uv run pytest
```
[% if background_tasks == "taskiq" or enable_caching or rate_limiting == "redis" %]
Redis 消费能力需要先启动共享实例：

```bash
docker compose up -d redis
```
[% endif %]
[% if background_tasks == "taskiq" %]
后台任务使用以下独立进程：

